es/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561030\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561030\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-7-810x1081.jpg\" alt=\"Modern glass and steel balcony extends from a concrete building, surrounded by green trees, with a view of a distant town and sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1081\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-7-810x1081.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-7-800x1068.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-7-768x1025.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-7-1151x1536.jpg 1151w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561031\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561031\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-8-810x607.jpg\" alt=\"Modern glass and steel building on stilts, set in a grassy landscape with trees in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"607\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-