ech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-13-810x1081.jpg\" alt=\"Concrete hallway with a ceiling light strip, leading to a glass door showing a tree and outdoor area.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1081\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-13-810x1081.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-13-800x1068.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-13-768x1025.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-13-1151x1536.jpg 1151w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOnce on the residential level, the villa’s layout unfolds with a sense of openness and warmth. A central living space features a cozy yet expansive living room, dining area, and kitchen that flow together, inviting residents and guests to move naturally through the home. This main area opens onto a south-facing terrace, which transitions into a lush, vegetated hillside where a swimming pool offers a retreat under the sun. The villa’s unique bridge design allows for additional separation between spaces, with children’s rooms situated on one side and the primary bedroom and bath, complete with views, on the other.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561037\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561037\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Villa-Sidonius-House-Czech-Stempel-Tesar-architekti-14-810x607.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with black cabinetry, a sleek island with built-in appliances, and a round dining table with matching chairs. Large windows offer a view of greenery outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"607\" srcset